E‑Commerce Sales Dashboard — Excel Project
An interactive Excel dashboard designed to analyze key e‑commerce performance metrics, identify sales trends, and support data‑driven decision‑making. This project demonstrates advanced Excel skills including Power Query, PivotTables, data modeling, dynamic formulas, and dashboard design.

Project Overview:
This project explores an e‑commerce dataset containing order details, customer information, product categories, and regional performance. The dashboard provides a consolidated view of business performance through automated KPIs and interactive visualizations.

The dashboard includes:

Total Sales, Profit, and Quantity Sold

Top‑performing product categories

Sales by region, segment, and customer type

Monthly and yearly sales trends

Order status breakdown

Profitability analysis by category and sub‑category

Tools & Techniques Used

Excel

Power Query for data cleaning and transformation

PivotTables & PivotCharts for aggregation and analysis

Slicers & Timelines for interactivity

Dynamic formulas (XLOOKUP, SUMIFS, FILTER, etc.)

Conditional formatting for visual insights

Dashboard layout design for clear storytelling
